課程概述 Course Description
       研習者可於課程中習得飛機修護計劃與修護管制之相關知識On completion of the lecture, the attendees will be familiar with the knowledge/skill of the Aircraft Maintenance Program and Aircraft Maintenance Control.

Course Outline:
（一）Aircraft Maintenance Program
1 Regulation requirements for Aircraft Maintenance Program
2. Evolution of Aircraft Maintenance Program
3. MRB (Maintenance Review Board) Process
4. MSG-3 Introduction
5.Development of Airline Aircraft Maintenance Program
6. Aircraft Maintenance Program Introduction
（二）Component Maintenance Program
（三）Aircraft Maintenance Control
1.Aircraft Layover Planning
2.Maintenance Control
    

課程學習目標 Course Objectives
課程中習得飛機修護計劃修護管制之相關知識修護計劃之演進過程及MSG-3簡介
 

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1飛機修護計劃2修護計劃與法規3修護計劃之演進過程4維護需求委員會5MSG-3簡介6航空公司飛機修護計劃制訂流程7飛機修護計劃簡介8飛機附件修護計劃9飛機修護管制10飛機修護排程11維護管制12飛機高階維修管理13完工檢討與分析14品質管理15品質管理之法源依據16品管組織及業務簡介17維修人員訓練及授權制度18品質檢驗與品質稽核 

